{"tid":2323130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩岸角力｜習近平認為已收服香港 全力施灰色戰術「陰乾」台灣","createTime":"2020-12-13T02:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T08:16:36.000Z","uid":19527,"like":113,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"e39fb3157713bb42da70b3988e49bfb2fb81e64c","tid":2323130,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201212/73XQQPFV7VAFDO4GMD4TOJBFWU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0YKQHVED7gHM1d6hG3GLtbdMyfy0wxcFSXfqjRWQtFNrqRwRA3dA4Anj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201212%2F73XQQPFV7VAFDO4GMD4TOJBFWU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0YKQHVED7gHM1d6hG3GLtbdMyfy0wxcFSXfqjRWQtFNrqRwRA3dA4Anj4&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=d1be681e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201212%2F73XQQPFV7VAFDO4GMD4TOJBFWU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0YKQHVED7gHM1d6hG3GLtbdMyfy0wxcFSXfqjRWQtFNrqRwRA3dA4Anj4&h=77070e23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201212/73XQQPFV7VAFDO4GMD4TOJBFWU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0YKQHVED7gHM1d6hG3GLtbdMyfy0wxcFSXfqjRWQtFNrqRwRA3dA4Anj4</a><br />\n<br />\n香港在疫情及《國安法》打壓下，持續一年的街頭抗爭基本平息。有外國媒體專題報道分析指，中共認為已收服香港對其管治的挑戰，已將矛頭轉向台灣，全力以「不動真格」的軍機擾台方式，以「灰色地帶」戰術（gray-zone warfare）「陰乾」台灣的抵抗實力與意志，達到征服台灣的目的。<br />\n<br />\n..........<br />\n<br />\n報道指，大陸在中共總書記領導之下，軍力急速發展。有分析人士認為解放軍征服台灣只需要一天的時間，而這也是中國的首要軍事任務。又指，隨着香港、新疆及西藏已被中共嚴密控制，台灣成為中共最後一個主要目標，而習近平去年曾在演講中表明，統一台灣雖無明確期限，但不排除使用武力。<br />\n報道引述台灣高級情報官員表示，今年是兩岸局勢的分水嶺，過去中共只是在理論性上不斷重覆武統，今年卻轉變為「辯論」及就可能出現的行動制定軍事計劃。<br />\n<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n據路透社根據政府數據計算，蔡英文政府計劃明年將國防開支增加10％以上，達到約160億美元（約1,240億港元），並加強對外購武和自研武器，以應付對岸的威脅。<br />\n美國退役陸戰隊上校Grant Newsham，去年多半時間留在台灣進行由台灣政府出資的台灣防禦能力評估計劃。現為日本戰略研究論壇（Japan Forum for Strategic Studies）研究員的他指出：「（台灣）軍隊已經裁軍。&hellip;&hellip;為保家衞國而戰，彷彿變成其他人的責任。」<br />\n5名美國退役高階指揮官告訴路透社，台灣把自己的命運置於華府手中，但美國及其盟友有可能會在台海之戰敗給中國，或者來不及馳援。"},{"pid":"8cfaad3de495f1c651b3c3674c271079e4bb38cc","tid":2323130,"uid":155095,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"習近平認為已經收復美國就真<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qEyiVWXly5Y/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FqEyiVWXly5Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d0703a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/179038/a1-1@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F179038%2Fa1-1%401200x1200.jpg&h=052ff49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/public/uploads/assets/2020/12/07/2020-12-07-5fcd73e7eec02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2020-12-07-5fcd73e7eec02.jpg&h=2a87633f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"683b8bd3048d4b471c8a9e17b275960fd5a127ac","tid":2323130,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a4574ba88692a7dc72094147b2b37a363631db","tid":2323130,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"815811e91d5784baed428639fcea8654d30d24a7","tid":2323130,"uid":93986,"like":133,"dislike":9,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"如果香港人要復仇就要幫台灣<br />\n因為香港已經玩完。<br />\n香港人要成立國際性抗共聯盟。"},{"pid":"a31baa4804e17a43d97151a34a474e2daa